            <h3 class="mb-1">Why people love using Easy Flags</h3>
            <p class="small muted">Simple, clear, and built for fast teams.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 mt-6">
            <div class="flex-1 feature-tile">
              <div class="feature-badge badge-accent">🚀</div>
              <div>
                <p class="small small-strong">Faster releases</p>
                <p class="small muted">Ship in smaller steps.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 feature-tile">
              <div class="feature-badge badge-green">🎯</div>
              <div>
                <p class="small small-strong">More control</p>
